                        <ul class="inner">
                            <li><a href="#" class="toggle">what is a business rates holiday for retail, hospitality and leisure businesses?</a><div class="inner"><p>Businesses in the retail, hospitality and leisure sectors in England will not have to pay business rates for the 2020 to 2021 tax year.</div></li>
                            <li>
                                <a href="#" class="toggle">
                                    Am I eligible for the business rates holiday for retail, hospitality and leisure businesses?
                                </a><div class="inner">
                                    <p>
                                        You’re eligible if your property is a:
                                        <ol>
