                        <a href="#" class="toggle">The Small Business Grant Fund (SBGF)</a>
                        <ul class="inner">
                            <li><a href="#" class="toggle">	What is the Small Business Grant Fund (SBGF)?	</a><div class="inner"><p>The Small Business Grant Fund (SBGF) supports small and rural businesses in England with their business costs during coronavirus. Small businesses in England which pay little or no business rates are entitled to a one-off cash grant of £10,000 from their local council.</div></li>
                            <li>
